article.description: — Jaxson Baker had 18 points in New Hampshire's 60-57 win over Maine on Saturday night.
article.headline: Baker scores 18 in New Hampshire's 60-57 victory over Maine
article.linkText: Baker scores 18 in New Hampshire's 60-57 victory over Maine
article.story: DURHAM, N.H. -- — Jaxson Baker had 18 points in New Hampshire's 60-57 win over Maine on Saturday night. Baker had 10 rebounds for the Wildcats (14-9, 6-4 America East Conference). Clarence O. Daniels II added 13 points and nine rebounds. Trey Woodyard scored 13 on 6-for-10 shooting. The Black Bears (11-13, 3-6) were led by Peter Filipovity with 20 points and eight rebounds. Jaden Clayton had 12 points and three steals. Kellen Tynes added 10 points and three steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
